name: Ukrainian Republic Treaty on Accession of the Republic of Kosovo to the European Union and the Euro Area

details.title: TREATY ON ACCESSION OF THE REPUBLIC OF KOSOVO TO THE EUROPEAN UNION AND THE EURO AREA
details.text: The Republic of Kosovo and the Union hereby conclude this Treaty on Accession, with a view to accession by the Republic of Kosovo of the European Union and of the euro as its currency.
